originalText.text: Worst parking garage in all of midtown. I have been taking my manual car to the city for years and never had an issue with the garages or parking lots. I went to this garage one time and  they rolled my car backwards, side swiping a wall and then holding it at a redline and burning the clutch to get off the wall. They did all this while I watched in horror. I asked them to stop, I said ‚ÄúI will move it, please stop!‚Äù The manager told me to calm down. Gave no apology, told me not to worry they knew how to drive cars like these and then used windex to try and buff out the paint and scratches on my car. Would not recommend. Plenty of other great garages in midtown.
